{"title":"一定要解放台湾","authors":["徐迟"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要解放台湾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐迟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九年的时间太长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九年没有见太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九年的苦难太深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九年不闻欢笑声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要解放台湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人们已等得太久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛已经望穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血也快叫吸血鬼吸干！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要解放台湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让台湾回入祖国胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让船只从基隆驶回祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让台北温泉洗净自己的屈辱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要解放台湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让阿里山森林恢复青翠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让苦痛的台糖重新发甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们的亲人也来建立公社。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同来审判蒋贼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后来庆祝国庆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这已经是时候了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要解放台湾！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}